* 0.5.0.0

  - started recording a CHANGELOG
  - use the new bytestring builder and the dropped function
    'renderHtmlToByteStringIO', as the new bytestring builder does
    not support 'toByteStringIO'. 
  - use &#34; instead of &quot; to escape a doublequote, thus saving one byte
    per escaping

  - removed deprecated functions from Text.Blaze: 
      text, lazyText, string, textValue, lazyTextValue, stringValue.
    Use Blaze.Html.toValue instead.
